snippet: Ukraine’s intelligence service has opened a new case against Yulia V. Tymoshenko, less than 48 hours after she was sentenced in a trial widely viewed as politically motivated.
lead_paragraph: Ukraine’s intelligence service has opened a new case against Yulia V. Tymoshenko, less than 48 hours after she was sentenced in a trial widely viewed as politically motivated.

headline.main: Former Ukrainian Premier Faces New Investigation
